---
title: Salisbury Beef and Pork Meatballs with Mushroom Gravy, Peas and Smashed Potatoes
description: Hearty mushroom gravy smothers tender beef-pork meatballs and comforting chive smashed potatoes in this modern take on Salisbury steak. In a word...YUM!
